data.description: This multi-level furnished condominium was designed with a modern style featuring four bedrooms with three and a half baths and large two-bay garage, perfect for entertaining. Built with quality finishes, white quartz counter tops throughout, energy-efficient appliances, lighting, heating and cooling systems that reduce energy costs for you as the homeowner. This home offers a very bright and open feeling with neutral tones across the wood laminate flooring. A great primary bedroom with ensuite, dual vanity sinks and big walk-in closet. Many enjoyable neighborhood amenities, like the large community recreational center, complete with a fitness gym, resort-style lap pool and spa. You can also relax at the poolside patio, clubhouse, or utilize the built in barbecues. There is also a rooftop lounge where you can enjoy an evening. Playa del sol is located north of State Route 905 and just east of Interstate 805 in Ocean View Hills, near excellent schools, neighborhood parks, shopping, dining and entertainment.This multi-level furnished condominium was designed with a modern style featuring four bedrooms with three and a half baths and large two-bay garage, perfect for entertaining.
